Package: detectseparation
Title: Detect or check for separation and infinite maximum likelihood estimates in generalized linear models with categorical responses
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Ioannis", family = "Kosmidis", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "ioannis.kosmidis@warwick.ac.uk", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1556-0302")),
             person(given = "Dirk", family = "Schumacher", role = "aut", email = "mail@dirk-schumacher.net"),
             person(given = "Kjell", family = "Konis", role = "ctb", email = "kjell.konis@me.com"))
Description: Provides pre-fit and post-fit methods for detecting separation and infinite maximum likelihood estimates in binomial response generalized linear models.
